  "title": "If the Weiss 2024 RCT found psilocybin and escitalopram moved openness equally at 6 months, could the 14-month persistence test distinguish them — does psilocybin's openness gain endure past 6 months where escitalopram's decays, or does the general therapeutic response persist equally?",
